{
  // Custom item parent for the Hacker Device. Derives from KeyMechanical
  // (5c99f98d86f7745c314214b3) so items using this parent inherit the
  // engine's KeyComponent — that's what gives us native NumberOfUsages
  // tracking + auto-discard at MaximumNumberOfUsage.
